title: Input, $$t$$
text: The inputs are $$t=0$$ and $$t=5$$, so $$0$$ seconds and $$5$$ seconds after the projectile.

title: Output
text: $$s(t)=height$$ of the projectile in feet, so $$s(0)=height$$ of the projectile in feet at $$t=0$$ and $$s(5)=height$$ of the projectile in feet at $$t=5$$.

title: Explanation
text: After $$0$$ seconds, the projectile is at a height of $$0$$ feet and after $$5$$ seconds, the projectile is at a height of $$0$$ feet again. Equivalently, the projectile begins at a height of $$0$$ feet and after $$5$$ seconds, is at $$0$$ feet again.
